---
import BaseThemeLayout from '@layouts/BaseThemeLayout.astro';
import AnimatedWaterBackground from '@components/ui/AnimatedWaterBackground.astro';
---

<BaseThemeLayout
  title="Funds as Instruments - The Water Foundation"
  description="Transforming how capital flows to create systemic water solutions through innovative fund structures"
  ogImage="/ogImageLandscape__The-Water-Foundation.jpg"
  ogImagePortrait="/ogImagePortrait__The-Water-Foundation.jpg"
>
  <main class="relative min-h-screen">
    <!-- Animated Water Background -->
    <AnimatedWaterBackground intensity="moderate" pattern="flowing" />
    
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative py-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-900 via-blue-800 to-cyan-800 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <div class="absolute top-20 left-20 w-96 h-96 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600/25 to-blue-600/20 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse-slow"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-32 right-32 w-80 h-80 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600/25 to-cyan-600/20 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse-delay"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/3 w-64 h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/20 to-blue-600/15 rounded-full blur-2xl animate-pulse-slow-2"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-medium mb-8 tracking-wide text-cyan-300">
          Funds as Instruments
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Transforming how capital flows to create systemic water solutions through innovative fund structures
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content Section -->
    <section class="relative py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-950 via-blue-900 to-indigo-900 overflow-hidden">
      <AnimatedWaterBackground intensity="subtle" pattern="scattered" />
      
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <!-- Introduction -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium mb-6 tracking-wide text-cyan-300">
            Our Open, Networked Approach.
          </h2>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/10 via-blue-500/10 to-indigo-500/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-cyan-400/30 rounded-2xl p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <p class="text-blue-100 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              <span class="block text-lg mb-2">Impact, Transformation, and Returns are hamstrung by a very siloed reality.</span>
              <span class="text-base">
                They only manage whatever kind of instrument or vehicle that they manage, they almost never have more than one fund structure instrument. Why? It's the way the industry grew up. It has always been. No other reason.
              </span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Funds as Instruments Section -->
        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/15 via-blue-500/15 to-indigo-500/15 backdrop-blur-sm border border-cyan-400/30 rounded-2xl p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-cyan-100 leading-tight">
                We believe funds are instruments of change.
              </p>
              <div class="flex justify-center py-2">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-cyan-400" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M12 5v14m0 0l-7-7m7 7l7-7"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-cyan-100 leading-tight">
                And we need a symphony of instruments to create the change we need.
              </p>
              <p class="text-blue-100 text-lg mt-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                Just as an orchestra combines strings, woodwinds, brass, and percussion to create beautiful music, we combine different fund structures—each with its unique purpose and approach—to create a harmonious and powerful force for water solutions. No single instrument can play every note, and no single fund structure can address every challenge. Our strength lies in this diversity and our ability to orchestrate these instruments in harmony.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Decorative Gradient Divider -->
        <div class="w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-cyan-400/30 to-transparent my-16"></div>
        
        <!-- The Water Foundation's Role -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium mb-6 tracking-wide text-cyan-300">
            The Water Foundation's Role
          </h2>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/10 via-blue-500/10 to-indigo-500/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-cyan-400/30 rounded-2xl p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <p class="text-blue-100 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              The Water Foundation serves as the conductor of this symphony, ensuring each instrument plays its part at the right time and in harmony with others. We don't just create funds—we create an ecosystem where different financial instruments can work together seamlessly, amplifying their collective impact far beyond what any single approach could achieve alone.
            </p>
            <p class="text-blue-100 leading-relaxed">
              Our role is to identify gaps in the funding landscape, design the right instruments to fill those gaps, and ensure they work in concert to create systemic change. We're not just building funds; we're building a new financial infrastructure for water sustainability.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Open Innovation Section -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/10 to-blue-500/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-cyan-400/20 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-cyan-200 mb-4">Open Innovation</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100 leading-relaxed">
              The belief and strategy that prioritizes the importance of external ideas, practices, and opportunities in driving innovation and growth. It recognizes that innovation is not a closed system, but rather a dynamic process that benefits from the exchange of ideas and knowledge across different organizations, sectors, industries, and even countries.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/10 to-indigo-500/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-blue-400/20 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-200 mb-4">Network Capital</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100 leading-relaxed">
              The belief and strategy that more value is created by the exchange of ideas and knowledge across different organizations, sectors, industries, and even countries, than by small teams of elite professionals working in relative isolation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Network Capital Approach -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium mb-8 tracking-wide text-cyan-300">
            Concieved and Designed to be Transformative through an Open, Networked Strategy.
          </h2>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
            <!-- Card 1 -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500/10 via-blue-500/10 to-cyan-500/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-indigo-400/20 rounded-2xl p-6 group hover:from-indigo-500/20 hover:to-cyan-500/20 transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-400 to-cyan-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 mx-auto group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">1</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-200 mb-3">Expert-Led Fund Management</h3>
              <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Different fund structures are managed by professionals with proven track records in their specific fund structure, supported by experienced trustees.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Card 2 -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/10 via-cyan-500/10 to-indigo-500/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-blue-400/20 rounded-2xl p-6 group hover:from-blue-500/20 hover:to-indigo-500/20 transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-indigo-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 mx-auto group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">2</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-200 mb-3">Fund Trusteeship</h3>
              <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Trustees ensure alignment with mission and values while generating outstanding impact and financial returns relative to alternatives.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Card 3 -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/10 via-indigo-500/10 to-blue-500/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-cyan-400/20 rounded-2xl p-6 group hover:from-cyan-500/20 hover:to-blue-500/20 transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-400 to-blue-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 mx-auto group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">3</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-cyan-200 mb-3">Mission Boards</h3>
              <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Special advisory boards initiate and oversee collective impact on specific challenges or efforts.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
            <!-- Card 4 -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500/10 to-cyan-500/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-indigo-400/20 rounded-2xl p-6 group hover:from-indigo-500/20 hover:to-cyan-500/20 transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-400 to-cyan-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 mx-auto group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">4</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-200 mb-3">Coalition Building</h3>
              <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Managing Partners form strategic coalitions across fund structures to address specific challenges, facilitated by Mission Boards and aligned with organizational goals.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Card 5 -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/10 to-indigo-500/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-blue-400/20 rounded-2xl p-6 group hover:from-blue-500/20 hover:to-indigo-500/20 transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-indigo-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 mx-auto group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">5</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-200 mb-3">Unified Coordination</h3>
              <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                The Water Foundation serves as the coordinating body, ensuring alignment, facilitating knowledge sharing, and driving collective impact across all initiatives.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Card 6 - 80% Width -->
          <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
            <div class="w-full max-w-4xl bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/10 via-blue-500/10 to-indigo-500/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-cyan-400/20 rounded-2xl p-8 group hover:from-cyan-500/20 hover:to-indigo-500/20 transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.01]">
              <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-6">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-400 to-blue-500 rounded-2xl flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                  <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">6</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-cyan-200 mb-3">Transparent Governance</h3>
                  <p class="text-blue-100 leading-relaxed">
                    The Board of Directors of the Water Foundation serves as the governing body, ensuring transparency and accountability. Board Meetings are default streamed to the public and archived (save executive sessions).
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

    
        <!-- Call to Action -->
        <div class="text-center mt-12">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/20 via-blue-500/20 to-indigo-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-cyan-400/30 rounded-2xl p-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-cyan-200 mb-4">Join the Movement</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6">
              Ready to be part of a new paradigm in impact investing? Explore how our innovative fund structures can amplify your impact.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
              <a href="/contact" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 hover:from-cyan-600 hover:to-blue-600 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg">
                Get in Touch
              </a>
              <a href="/strategy" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/20 to-indigo-500/20 hover:from-blue-500/30 hover:to-indigo-500/30 text-blue-300 font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-xl border border-blue-400/30 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg">
                Our Strategy
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseThemeLayout>

<style>
  /* Smooth transitions for all elements */
  * {
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  /* Animation for the background gradient */
  @keyframes gradient-shift {
    0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
    100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
  }
  
  .gradient-animate {
    background-size: 200% 200%;
    animation: gradient-shift 15s ease infinite;
  }
</style>
